PERFECTLY.

94
00:03:56,153 --> 00:03:58,322
RICK:
YOU PRETENDED TO BE MY FRIEND.

95
00:04:01,366 --> 00:04:02,326
AAAHHHHHHH!

96
00:04:13,712 --> 00:04:14,796
HATZILAKOS:
I'D LIKE TO ANNOUNCE

97
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,882
THAT OUT OF THE MANY PROPOSALS
SUBMITTED,

98
00:04:16,965 --> 00:04:18,842
THE WINNER IS...

99
00:04:18,926 --> 00:04:20,302
A NEW MURAL,

100
00:04:20,385 --> 00:04:22,888
