A GOOD ARTIST,

108
00:04:38,779 --> 00:04:40,614
AND WITH THE SHOOTING...

109
00:04:40,697 --> 00:04:41,740
WE JUST THOUGHT
IT WAS RIGHT.

110
00:04:43,242 --> 00:04:43,951
CRAIG:
GOOD JOB, MAN.

111
00:04:44,034 --> 00:04:45,118
JIMMY:
THANK YOU.

112
00:04:45,202 --> 00:04:47,120
CRAIG:
THIS IS GREAT.

113
00:04:47,204 --> 00:04:48,789
SO TELL ME...

114
00:04:48,872 --> 00:04:52,709
WHEN DID JIMMY AND ELLIE
BECOME A "WE"?

115
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,885
CRAIG:
SOMEONE LEFT YOU A CARD.

116
00:05:01,969 --> 00:05:02,803
HOW SWEET.

117
00:05:03,387 --> 00:05:07,224
SPINNER:
IT'S A NOTE, MAN,
FROM MY GIRLFRIEND.

118
00:05:07,891 --> 00:05:08,892
HEY, JIMMY,

119
00:05:08,976 --> 00:05:10,686
CONGRATULATIONS, MAN. EH?

120
00:05:10,769 --> 00:05:13,856
LISTEN, I WANT TO HELP OUT
IF THERE IS ANYTHING I CAN DO.

121
00:05:13,939 --> 00:05:15,023
WHATEVER.

122
00:05:15,107 --> 00:05:16,942
