SPIN.

123
00:05:17,025 --> 00:05:18,777
SPINNER:
COME ON, GUYS.
LET ME HELP OUT.

124
00:05:19,987 --> 00:05:22,281
LOOK, WHEN I SAID
YOU WERE DEAD TO ME,

125
00:05:22,364 --> 00:05:23,699
I MEANT FOREVER.

126
00:05:24,867 --> 00:05:26,201
YOU DON'T EXIST.

127
00:05:38,422 --> 00:05:40,507
SO, THIS WEEKEND?

128
00:05:40,591 --> 00:05:43,010
YOU, ME,
DOZENS OF HORNY HONEYS,

129
00:05:43,093 --> 00:05:46,471
