136
00:05:58,192 --> 00:06:00,611
AND JIMMY?
WE HELPED HIM TOO, RIGHT?

137
00:06:00,694 --> 00:06:02,529
SPIN,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

138
00:06:02,613 --> 00:06:05,032
YOU'RE GETTING YOURSELF
ALL DEPRESSED!

139
00:06:05,115 --> 00:06:07,367
