MIND OFF THE DEPRESSING CRAP.

141
00:06:11,038 --> 00:06:12,706
HAVE SOME FUN.

142
00:06:16,793 --> 00:06:19,213
DUDE,
YOU ARE SO RIGHT.

143
00:06:27,387 --> 00:06:28,388
