182
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:21,168
YOU'RE KIDDING.
THAT'S AMAZING.

183
00:08:21,251 --> 00:08:22,753
ELLIE:
IT'S A JOB.

184
00:08:22,836 --> 00:08:24,505
